NFT holders get to decide the story arc of the show through on-chain voting in a Choose-Your-Own-Adventure style poll at the end of each weekly episode. NFT holders will be able to engage with other holders through the DIC punch, an on chain social action, and also have access to contribute to the Gimmicks wiki which will house the complete lore of the Gimmicks world.
